name: Robert Pattinson Breaks Down His Most Iconic Characters | GQ
description:
"I spent a lot of time living off the Harry Potter money." Robert Pattinson breaks down his most iconic roles, including his characters in 'Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire,' 'Twilight,' 'The Batman,' 'Good Time,' 'The Lighthouse,' 'Tenet,' 'Cosmopolis,' 'High Life,' 'The Rover' and that time he desperately needed a New York City hot dog (https://youtu.be/9kdy6IpoHEI).
